high_descs: Go to the small table straight ahead and slightly to the left.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right and go to the sofa that is ahead and to the right.
Slice the potato that is next to the darker colored food on the left side of the sofa.
Look to the closer end of the sofa where the tomato is.
Put the knife down on the sofa next to the tomato.
Look back to the sliced potato.
Pick up one potato slice.
Turn left and then left again towards the hallway, taking the first doorway on the left towards the bed.
Place the potato slice into the empty, lighter colored pot that is against the wall on the bed.
Pick up that pot from the bed.
Return to the table that you got the knife from.
Put the pot down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a potato slice in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left to head to the dining table.
Pick up the knife from the dining table.
Turn around and head left to reach the sofa.
Cut the potato on the sofa into slices with the knife.
Turn to reach the sofa.
Put the knife on the sofa.
Turn to face the potato on the sofa.
Pick up the slice of potato from the sofa.
Turn around and head to the bed room on the left to reach the bed.
Put the slice of potato in the pan at the back.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn around to exit the room and head right to reach the dining table.
Put the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the slice of potato on the dining table.

high_descs: Stand up turn around walk towards the dining table.
Pick up the knife from the dining table.
Turn around walk towards the sofa.
Cut the potato into pieces.
Turn around towards the sofa.
Keep the knife on the top of the sofa.
Turn around move towards the sofa.
Pick up the potato from the sofa.
Turn around walk towards the pot.
Put the potato on the pot.
Pick up the pot with the potato on it.
Turn around walk towards the dining table.
Keep the pot on the top of the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the pot with the piece of potato on it and keep it on dining table.
